Convert radians to degrees

Source: R/utils.R
rad_to_deg.Rd

Convert radians to degrees

rad_to_deg(rad)

Arguments

rad

A vector of values, in radians, to convert to decimal degrees

Value

A vector of the same length in decimal degrees

See also

Other utilities: add_bbox_buffer(), calc_haversine_distance(), convert_distance(), deg_to_rad(), get_bbox_centroid(), get_coord_bbox(), point_from_distance()

Examples

rad_to_deg(2 * base::pi)

#> [1] 360
rad_to_deg(deg_to_rad(360))

#> [1] 360
